lead_paragraph: Fresh from victory at the European Tour's Abu Dhabi Championship on Sunday, globe-trotting American Rickie Fowler will be targeting his fifth title in just eight months at this week's Farmers Insurance Open outside San Diego.

headline.print_headline: Fowler Eyes Fifth Win in Eight Months, at Torrey Pines
